These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, december
1. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |
| Birthday   | december | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret
1. the owner of the ferret is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |
| Pet   | lizard | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-4-3::.
